data.name: Allan Chemical Corporation
data.description:
Allan Chemical Corporation has been a leading chemical distributor since 1984, sourcing specialty chemicals and raw ingredients from well respected manufacturers around the globe. Allan Chemical's customer oriented, full service approach has led to long lasting relationships with customers and partners.


Our formula is simple: we combine reliable access to high-grade chemical raw materials with an approach that places the customer at the heart of everything we do. Allan Chemical's success has always been built on the core values we live by: trust, honesty, quality, hard work, and service. Allan Chemical Corporation is more than just a company; we are people who believe that your business is our business. Our growth and success are a result of our ability to respond to customer requirements with products that meet their specifications.


Our products include flavor and fragrance ingredients, pharmaceutical intermediates and excipients, laboratory reagents, plasticizers, lubricants for plastics and tableting applications, chemicals for silk-screen cleaning and electronics manufacturing, among other industries.


ï»¿We are not responsible for errors or typos. Availability and pricing are subject to change.
